---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Dixon Painting Co."
  description="Privacy policy for Dixon Painting Co. — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="legal-hero__headline">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-hero__sub">Last updated: April 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-content">
    <div class="container legal-content__inner">
      <div class="legal-prose">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>Dixon Painting Co. ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website <strong>dixonpaintingco.com</strong>. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our site and contact us for services.</p>
        <p>By using this site, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. We take your privacy seriously and only collect information necessary to respond to your service inquiries.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide voluntarily when you fill out our contact or estimate request forms:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Name</strong> — to address you properly when we respond</li>
          <li><strong>Phone number</strong> — to reach you to schedule your estimate</li>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> — to send you estimate details or follow-up information</li>
          <li><strong>Service type</strong> — to understand what kind of help you need</li>
          <li><strong>Project details</strong> — any description of your project you choose to share</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not collect payment information through this website. All payment is handled in-person or by phone.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information you provide solely to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your estimate or service request</li>
          <li>Schedule on-site estimates</li>
          <li>Follow up on submitted requests</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your project</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>Form Submissions</h2>
        <p>Our contact forms are processed through <a href="https://www.netlify.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Netlify</a>. Form submissions are stored in our Netlify account and accessible only to authorized Dixon Painting Co. personnel. Netlify's privacy practices are governed by their own <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">privacy policy</a>.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>This website may use basic analytics tools to understand how visitors use our site (e.g., which pages are most visited). We do not use tracking cookies for advertising or retargeting purposes. Any analytics data collected is aggregate and anonymous.</p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain form submission data for as long as necessary to fulfill your service request and for a reasonable period thereafter for business records. You may request deletion of your information at any time by contacting us directly.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request a copy of the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of any inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for us to contact you</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the phone number or address below.</p>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. Our website uses HTTPS encryption for all data transmission.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your information, contact us:</p>
        <address class="legal-contact">
          <strong>Dixon Painting Co.</strong><br />
          Dixon, CA<br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:+19166122126" aria-label="Call Dixon Painting Co. at (916) 612-2126">(916) 612-2126</a>
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-hero { background: var(--color-primary); padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
  .legal-hero__headline { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-hero__sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.875rem; }

  .legal-content { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; background: #fff; }
  .legal-content__inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .legal-prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-prose p { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.975rem; }
  .legal-prose ul { margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .legal-prose li { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.65; font-size: 0.975rem; }
  .legal-prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal-contact { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.975rem; }
</style>
